{"tid":2509874,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一返工覺得自己係垃圾","createTime":"2021-04-29T17:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T18:48:41.000Z","uid":158103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b49a5b811abcd9e85e9d8acef3d5f9852aa2d372","tid":2509874,"uid":158103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"我一直做緊垃圾sell屎<br />\n而家半公半私 實質私佣係分勁撚少<br />\n導致個人返工日撚日係到發夢 仲要同事好好乜都唔洗我做<br />\n覺得自己係一件人形大垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019a722c9bbbca9683e6eaef06b5284a5d8d0a20","tid":2509874,"uid":98387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"返工唔洗做有錢收仲想點"},{"pid":"ac260a8fb566f99d2c971ec5d6b23d5cccb1171e","tid":2509874,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T17:58:26.000Z","msg":"有糧出理得佢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99a33d38fadedd5490bb1a8ccaec26adbfbb1d4","tid":2509874,"uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T18:00:55.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係, 返工成日要食屎 (因為係管理層)<br />\n但睇到上面的留言<br />\n我覺得, 我睇通左, 只要有錢收<br />\n其實你都係又價值的!"},{"pid":"d7b1048c0d8217400828e18803caa8f204eea751","tid":2509874,"uid":185631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T18:02:49.000Z","msg":"工作就只係一份收錢的工作<br />\n唔好太上心<br />\n同能力唔關事<br />\n因為好多公司又要慳錢, 又要請人, 到頭來請冇能力的人<br />\n唔係話你冇能力, 係你的能力等於這個價錢<br />\n既然係講錢, 就唔好同份工講感情!"},{"pid":"355b425dc755f697bf6ead4ef8d7e254e19df4a6","tid":2509874,"uid":221773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T18:06:57.000Z","msg":"揀咗份自己鍾意嘅工,但發覺自己做唔嚟真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年資低過我嘅好似仲多經驗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25595ca308e3faf3d96c6730089bedc9c1045c3b","tid":2509874,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"355b425dc755f697bf6ead4ef8d7e254e19df4a6","tid":250